  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Our Holidays</span></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13089502/our-holidays-838x320.jpg" alt="About Us" data-udi="umb://media/f13efac9d1664878b71848f09aea0cb0" /></p>
<p>Whether it’s Summer, Ski or Lapland, all of our holidays are based on your passions and interests, in the places we know best. Our destinations include Austria, Andorra, <a data-udi="umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3}" title="Canada">C</a>anada, France, Italy, Lapland, Madeira, Slovenia and Switzerland. All holidays are flexible with a choice of flight times, local airports, durations, multi-centre stays, accommodation and activities.</p>
<h2><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Our History</span></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13089503/ingham-skiier-838x220.jpg" alt="Inghams History" data-udi="umb://media/ec1127fb14004fdca26fbe82cc387993" /></p>
<div>Our founder, Walter Inghams, was so passionate about skiing, mountaineering and walking, he couldn’t help but share it. He pioneered the ski holiday and is famous as “the man who took Britain skiing.”</div>
<p>Over 85 years later, we’re one of the most trusted and respected special interest holiday companies in the UK. Walter’s vision is still alive today and we’re more excited than ever to be sharing ideas and inspiration for the perfect holiday. Whatever people feel passionately about, we know a place they’ll love.</p>
<h2><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Our Service</span><span style="text-decoration: underline;"></span></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13089496/our-serice-838x220.jpg" alt="Inghams Service" data-udi="umb://media/469a1968e5e2445ab92a2658ff08c0e1" /></p>
<p>From the reservations team who help you book your holiday to the overseas team who greet you at the airport and in resort, our people are passionate about our holidays and ensuring you have the best experience possible. Before, during and after your holiday, our team are only ever a phone call away.</p>
<p><iframe width="100%" height="450" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/TXU1afJpIdg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen="" title="YouTube video player"></iframe></p>
<h3><strong>Before your holiday</strong></h3>
<div class="g6">
<p>During the booking process and after you have booked, you have the help and support of our reservations team via phone, email and web chat. As well as pre-departure emails with useful information regarding your upcoming holiday.</p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="g6">
<p><img style="width: 400px; height: 200px;" src="/media/13089504/italy-summer-lake-woman-400x200.jpg?width=400&amp;height=200" alt="Before your Holiday" data-udi="umb://media/72fb7b1ed8a14f52af406e7a8cd214e1" /></p>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<h3>Whilst you're on holiday</h3>
<p>You will have the reassurance of a resort representative, either in resort or over the phone. Whether you require assistance or advice regarding your accommodation, transfers or in resort information, we are available and happy to help, you’re never on your own. Should an emergency arise in resort, such as a serious injury or illness and there is no representative present in your resort, we will do our very best to arrange for a member of the team to be with you in person, just as soon as we possibly can.</p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="g6">
<p><img style="width: 400px; height: 200px;" src="/media/13089505/inghams-winter-lapland-skidoo-400x200.jpg?width=400&amp;height=200" alt="Whilst your on holiday" data-udi="umb://media/cf17e11313b4444f8fbfdb37f8992d90" /></p>
<p> </p>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<h3>When you return from your holiday</h3>
<p>Our guest relations team are available via phone, email and web chat to hear your feedback and assist with any queries you may have.</p>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<p><img style="width: 400px; height: 200px;" src="/media/13089506/adobestock_175086751-rt2.jpg?width=400&amp;height=200" alt="Return home" data-udi="umb://media/a318d4bf0bbc498a959b7ed9645fb48d" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
</div>
<div class="g12">
<div>
<h2><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Sustainability</span></h2>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><img src="/media/13089498/sustainability-838x220.jpg" alt="Sustainability" data-udi="umb://media/621a2c3bdeff49908c676f8c098a981b" /></span></p>
<p>Here at Inghams, we believe in working with nature, not against it. That's why we're determined to become more environmentally friendly. Join us in our journey to become a sustainable business.</p>
<div class="g4">
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="tablet-button" style="height: 23px; width: 204px; background-color: #ffffff; border-color: #f26419; float: left;">
<tbody>
<tr style="height: 22px;">
<td width="auto" height="16" align="center" valign="center" style="background-color: #f26419; border-radius: 4px; background-clip: padding-box; padding-left: 14px; padding-right: 14px; text-align: center; height: 22px; width: 203px;"><a style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none;" data-udi="umb://document/67e40dbb55ff45098496ea2e7eee1f72" href="/{localLink:umb://document/67e40dbb55ff45098496ea2e7eee1f72}" title="Sustainability"><strong>Find out more</strong></a></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p> </p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Our Reassurance</span></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13089499/ish-838x220.jpg" alt="In Safe Hands Inghams" data-udi="umb://media/09a2dc2698774dbe98cc06fd1c229401" /></p>
<p>You're In Safe Hands when you book with us. We are committed to doing the right thing by our customers. We always keep the customer at the heart of our decisions ensuring you can book with confidence.</p>
<p>Visit our <a data-udi="umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae}" title="In Safe Hands">In Safe Hands</a> page for more information about the extra measures we have put in place to protect you before, during and after your holiday.</p>
<div class="g4">
<p><img src="/media/13085394/refund.png" alt="Covid-19 refund promise" /></p>
<p><strong>Covid-19 refund promise</strong></p>
<p>If things change and we have to cancel your holiday because of Covid, you can pick another trip, or get a full refund.</p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><img src="/media/13085393/protection.png" alt="ATOL &amp; ABTA protection" /></p>
<p><strong>ATOL &amp; ABTA protection</strong></p>
<p>These schemes are backed by the government, so whatever happens, your money is protected.</p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><img src="/media/13085396/strong.png" alt="We’re in a strong position" /></p>
<p><strong>We’re in a strong position</strong></p>
<p>We’re part of a much bigger family of businesses. Our parent company is a large Swiss supermarket and retailer called Migros, so as a group, we’re stronger together.</p>
</div>]]></bodyText>
